    "body": "Try using the decimal type;\r\n\r\n[decimal]1 % 0.1 = 0.0\r\n\r\n[decimal]1 % 0.8 = 0.2\r\n\r\n[decimal]1 % 0.9 = 0.1\r\n\r\nIf you use the [decimal] type, you will get the expected outcome.",
